owercase, hyphens only\n- Output raw JSON only — no preamble, no markdown fences, no explanation\n\nPHASE 1 — PROPOSAL:\nBefore generating JSON, output a plain-English proposal summary prefixed with PROPOSAL:\nList the blueprint name, forms, schemas, email approach, and agent focus.\nEnd with: \"Reply CONFIRM to generate the full blueprint JSON.\"\n\nPHASE 2 — GENERATION:\nWhen input contains CONFIRM, output the complete JSON only.\n\nVALIDATION:\nAfter generating, append a VALIDATION: block listing any issues found. If none, write VALIDATION: PASSED.', '2026-06-09 21:29:42', '2026-06-09 21:29:42') made by require('wp-load.php'), require_once('wp-config.php'), require_once('wp-settings.php'), do_action('init'), WP_Hook->do_action, WP_Hook->apply_filters, SovereignBuilder->init, do_action('sb_modules_register'), WP_Hook->do_action, WP_Hook->apply_filters, SB_Blueprint_Builder::init, SB_Blueprint_Builder::seed, SB_Blueprint_Builder::seed_agent
